## M15b.1 per GPT-5.5 post-impl review entry 41: unbound type
## name in a type annotation fires a Rig diagnostic.
##
## Pre-M15b.1 this silently returned `invalid_id` and let the
## use site cascade to a type-mismatch (or compile-fine
## depending on flow). With the M22.1+M15b "unknown is poison"
## invariant lifted to the type system, type-position unbound
## must error at decl time so users see the root cause.

sub main()
  x: NopeType = 1
  print(x)
